Claude Code

===========================================================================

To run:
claude --dangerously-skip-permissions

Later, there will be an "auto mode" as an alternative to --dangerously-skip-permissions:
claude --enable-auto-mode

===========================================================================

To install:

curl -fsSL https://claude.ai/install.sh | bash
claude plugin install code-review@claude-plugins-official                     

npx ctx7 setup
npx ctx7 login

----------------

To update:
claude update

To diagnose:
claude doctor

===========================================================================

LSP support:

(See file build-lsp for non-Claude-specific installation.)

* Java instructions at: https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/jdtls-lsp
* C instructions at: https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/clangd-lsp
* bash:

cd ~/bin/install
wget -O jdt-language-server-latest.tar.gz https://www.eclipse.org/downloads/download.php?file=/jdtls/snapshots/jdt-language-server-latest.tar.gz

